SIMPLE: causeless
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Causeless
<hw>Cause"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>1. Self-originating;
uncreated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Without just or sufficient reason;
groundless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My fears are <qex>causeless</qex> and ungrounded.</q>
<rj><qau>Denham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Causeless</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Causeless
<hw>Cause"less</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Without cause or
reason.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Causelessness</ent>⟦br⟧
